description: Flying Pig Branding Co. is a full-service creative and strategic branding consultancy that works with clients and agencies. With over sixty years of combined experience, Flying Pig Branding has worked with clients in nearly every industry, small, medium, large, global, regional and local. Our experience is proven, results-oriented and award-winning.
